essdate=2021-11-29 |archive-date=2021-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129011633/http://district.ce.cn/newarea/sddy/201609/01/t20160901_15499587.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年8月，怀化市人民检察院依法以涉嫌受贿罪、挪用公款罪对湖南日报报业集团原党组副书记、总经理皮林提起公诉。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com//2017-08/09/c_1121457956.htm |title=湖南日报社原总经理皮林被提起公诉-新华网 |accessdate=2021-11-29 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524161858/http://www.xinhuanet.com//2017-08/09/c_1121457956.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

